lead_paragraph: Jeff Driskel and Jacoby Brissett once battled for a starting spot at Florida. Now, they're competing on opposite sides of the Senior Bowl in a game that's more about impressing NFL teams than who starts — or even who wins.

headline.print_headline: QBs, Top Prospects Take Different Routes to Senior Bowl
